<br>
There are several places in the mines that have Luggalds. So far I haven't seen any that are single or double spawns. There's a 3 spawn in the room between water tunnels, a 4 spawn in the pond cave, a multi-spawn in a room somewhere, and way down deep there is a huge cavern with tons of luggalds and dreadswords all packed together in groups around fires (instant 30 mob death if you aggro). Sorry I don't have loc for any of these, just been running around invis exploring. To my knowledge and experience today nothing in the Mines zone sees invis, so you are totally safe when using Veil of Elements, just watch that 10 minutes so you don't invis at a bad time. I ran out to the bridge/lava area to re-invis each time as it's big enough that you can get to the sides and not aggro anything regardless of level. Also as a point of info, I have found nothing in the water tunnels, so don't panic if you fall through that pit into the water, it's even a good place to re-invis but you will need a waterstone to get out or you'll drown.<br>
<br>
